column5: Nice fish, I miss hitting up Haliburton bass!
real nice fish
NICE FISH!! I just might have to plan a trip up the this fall, it's been a while. Congrats!
Awesome.
Nice fish man! The big girls really turned on this weekend! Congrats, thats a hawg!
Thats a really nice Bucket By the looks she'd be 6lbs+ i bet. Congrats !!!
Nice Shawn... great to see you posting again, let alone with some great Muskie food !
Nice fish
Real nice fish Shawn  Looks like you've lost some weight my friend
I got a nice 19" largemouth on the koopers frog. Its my new fav frog. Got 2 muskies on it too. Still going strong. Just have to squeeze out the water every few casts. Nice bass btw
Nice bucket Mr. Devil. Congrats.
Shawn...congrats on the new PB.  It's a monster!
Very nice, great fish!
What a hawg!  Well done!
Nice fish!  Congrates on the new PB
Great colours on her. That's a donkey
Nice job there Shawn. Thanks for posting, for sure there is more good ones you will catch.
nice fish...congrats on the pb
what a PIG!  Great fish.  LOVE the senko.  I bet it was wacky rigged?
Thats is a duke! Well done!  Joe

Awesome Hali bucket...I'm heading back up in a few days-here's the best from my last trip.  She came out of 20' dropshotting.  I'm glad to hear they've finally moved to more traditional summer haunts.
